<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="123" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1452,1360,1854]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bosch (van den Bosch" authorityYear="1858" box="[136,346,1398,1422]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Trichomanes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dregei">
<emphasis box="[136,346,1398,1422]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">Trichomanes dregei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, described on the basis of South African specimens, is listed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Roux, J. P." box="[1010,1144,1398,1422]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="1 - 293" refId="ref4571" refString="Roux, J. P. (2009) Synopsis of the Lycopodiophyta and Pteridophyta of Africa, Madagascar and neighbouring islands. Strelitzia 23: 1 - 293." type="journal article" year="2009">Roux (2009)</bibRefCitation>
as synonym for 
<taxonomicName authority="(Swartz 1788: 137) Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson (Ebihara et al. 2006: 243)" authorityName="Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson (Ebihara et al." authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="Swartz" baseAuthorityYear="1788" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rigidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">Abrodictyum rigidum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Swartz, O. P." box="[236,429,1434,1458]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" refId="ref4631" refString="Swartz, O. P. (1788) Nova genera &amp; species plantarum seu Prodromus. M. Swederi, Stockholm, Upsala &amp; Turku (Aboa), 152 pp." type="book" year="1788">Swartz 1788: 137</bibRefCitation>
) Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson (
<bibRefCitation author="Ebihara, A. &amp; Dubuisson, J. - Y. &amp; Iwatsuki, K. &amp; Hennequin, S. &amp; Ito, M." box="[694,963,1434,1458]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="221 - 280" refId="ref4184" refString="Ebihara, A., Dubuisson, J. - Y., Iwatsuki, K., Hennequin, S. &amp; Ito, M. (2006) A taxonomic revision of the Hymenophyllaceae. Blumea 51: 221 - 280. https: // doi. org / 10.3767 / 000651906 X 622210" type="journal article" year="2006">
Ebihara 
<emphasis box="[787,842,1434,1458]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">et al.</emphasis>
2006: 243
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. But the latter species is strictly Neotropical and the Afro-Malagasy populations actually represent the distinct taxon 
<taxonomicName authority="Bauret &amp; Dubuisson (Dubuisson et al. 2016: 161)" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudorigidum">
<emphasis box="[906,1096,1470,1494]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. pseudorigidum</emphasis>
Bauret &amp; Dubuisson (
<bibRefCitation author="Dubuisson, J. - Y. &amp; Bauret, L. &amp; Grall, A. &amp; Li, T. &amp; Ebihara, A. &amp; Hennequin, S." pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="151 - 168" refId="ref3972" refString="Dubuisson, J. - Y., Bauret, L., Grall, A., Li, T., Ebihara, A. &amp; Hennequin, S. (2016) Discussion on the taxonomy of African fern Abrodictyum rigidum (Sw.) Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson and description of two new Abrodictyum C. Presl species (Hymenophyllaceae, Polypodiidae) for the Afro-Malagasy region. Phytotaxa 284: 151 - 168. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 284.3.1" type="journal article" year="2016">
Dubuisson 
<emphasis box="[136,190,1506,1530]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">et al.</emphasis>
2016: 161
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1452,1360,1854]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">
Van den 
<bibRefCitation author="Bosch, R. B. van den" box="[288,436,1542,1566]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="341 - 419" refId="ref3629" refString="Bosch, R. B. van den (1858 [1859]) Synopsis Hymenophyllacearum, monographiae hujus ordinis prodromus. Nederlandsch kruidkundig archief 4: 341 - 419. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 41482" type="journal article" year="1858">Bosch (1858)</bibRefCitation>
named 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bosch (van den Bosch" authorityYear="1858" box="[526,622,1542,1566]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Trichomanes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dregei">
<emphasis box="[526,622,1542,1566]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">T. dregei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the South African specimens collected by Drège as cited by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kunze, G." box="[1301,1452,1542,1566]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="480 - 570" refId="ref4378" refString="Kunze, G. (1836) Plantarum acotyledonearum Africae australis recensio nova. Linnaea 10: 480 - 570." type="journal article" year="1836">Kunze (1836)</bibRefCitation>
under 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson (Ebihara et al." authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="Swartz" baseAuthorityYear="1788" box="[205,316,1578,1602]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rigidum">
<emphasis box="[205,316,1578,1602]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">T. rigidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, hence the Roux’ treatment. However, neither van den 
<bibRefCitation author="Bosch, R. B. van den" box="[916,1062,1578,1602]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="341 - 419" refId="ref3629" refString="Bosch, R. B. van den (1858 [1859]) Synopsis Hymenophyllacearum, monographiae hujus ordinis prodromus. Nederlandsch kruidkundig archief 4: 341 - 419. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 41482" type="journal article" year="1858">Bosch (1858)</bibRefCitation>
nor 
<bibRefCitation author="Kunze, G." box="[1114,1262,1578,1602]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="480 - 570" refId="ref4378" refString="Kunze, G. (1836) Plantarum acotyledonearum Africae australis recensio nova. Linnaea 10: 480 - 570." type="journal article" year="1836">Kunze (1836)</bibRefCitation>
accompanied the new name and citation of occurrence with a precise description. This explains that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bosch (van den Bosch" authorityYear="1858" box="[1037,1132,1614,1638]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Trichomanes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dregei">
<emphasis box="[1037,1132,1614,1638]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">T. dregei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
had been erroneously treated as a 
<emphasis box="[187,339,1650,1674]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">nomen nudum</emphasis>
in the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Dubuisson et al. 2016)" baseAuthorityName="Dubuisson" baseAuthorityYear="2016" box="[567,1028,1650,1674]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudorigidum">
<emphasis box="[567,759,1650,1674]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. pseudorigidum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Dubuisson, J. - Y. &amp; Bauret, L. &amp; Grall, A. &amp; Li, T. &amp; Ebihara, A. &amp; Hennequin, S." box="[774,1020,1650,1674]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="151 - 168" refId="ref3972" refString="Dubuisson, J. - Y., Bauret, L., Grall, A., Li, T., Ebihara, A. &amp; Hennequin, S. (2016) Discussion on the taxonomy of African fern Abrodictyum rigidum (Sw.) Ebihara &amp; Dubuisson and description of two new Abrodictyum C. Presl species (Hymenophyllaceae, Polypodiidae) for the Afro-Malagasy region. Phytotaxa 284: 151 - 168. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 284.3.1" type="journal article" year="2016">
Dubuisson 
<emphasis box="[898,954,1650,1674]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. This resulted from the oversight of an additional Kunze’s observation (p. 554) clearly mentioning a few morphological differences between Drège’s specimens and the Neotropical populations. As such, this observation should be considered as an effectively published diagnosis, to which van den 
<bibRefCitation author="Bosch, R. B. van den" box="[305,452,1758,1782]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="341 - 419" refId="ref3629" refString="Bosch, R. B. van den (1858 [1859]) Synopsis Hymenophyllacearum, monographiae hujus ordinis prodromus. Nederlandsch kruidkundig archief 4: 341 - 419. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 41482" type="journal article" year="1858">Bosch (1858)</bibRefCitation>
made a reference and thus validated the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bosch (van den Bosch" authorityYear="1858" box="[970,1066,1758,1782]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Trichomanes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dregei">
<emphasis box="[970,1066,1758,1782]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">T. dregei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Art. 38.1(a), 
<bibRefCitation author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[1226,1440,1758,1782]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" refId="ref4943" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Regnum Vegetabile 159. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis box="[1318,1374,1758,1782]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
). Since 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bosch (van den Bosch" authorityYear="1858" box="[201,293,1794,1818]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Trichomanes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dregei">
<emphasis box="[201,293,1794,1818]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">T. dregei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the earlier name, its specific epithet has priority over 
<taxonomicName authority="Bauret &amp; Dubuisson (Dubuisson et al. 2016: 161)" box="[880,1040,1794,1818]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudorigidum">
<emphasis box="[880,1040,1794,1818]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">pseudorigidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and must therefore be combined under 
<taxonomicName authority="C. Presl (Presl 1843: 20)" authorityName="C. Presl (Presl" authorityYear="1843" box="[136,539,1830,1854]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Hymenophyllaceae" genus="Abrodictyum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hymenophyllales" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[136,273,1830,1854]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">Abrodictyum</emphasis>
C.Presl (
<bibRefCitation author="Presl, C. B." box="[371,530,1830,1854]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" refId="ref4490" refString="Presl, C. B. (1843) Hymenophyllaceae. Eine botanische Abhandlung. G. Haase, Prague, 264 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 627" type="book" year="1843">Presl 1843: 20</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
